# CODEOWNERS - auto-assign reviewers and enforce review on sensitive paths.
# Combined with "Require review from Code Owners" in branch protection, this
# forces the right eyes on changes to the listed areas.

# Everything has a default owner
*                                   @NX1X

# Security-critical: CI, supply chain, org policy
/.github/                           @NX1X
/.github/workflows/                 @NX1X
/SECURITY.md                        @NX1X

# Egress enforcer + network eBPF - requires a network-security review
/internal/enforcer/                 @NX1X
/internal/bpf/network.bpf.c         @NX1X
/internal/bpf/                      @NX1X
/internal/collector/                @NX1X

# The published GitHub Action surface
/action/                            @NX1X

# Dependency + build policy
/go.mod                             @NX1X
/go.sum                             @NX1X
/docs/DEPENDENCIES.md               @NX1X
/Makefile                           @NX1X
